{"id": "1262575209844838553", "channel_id": "1221527962495484015", "type": 0, "author_id": "1168864875943055370", "author_name": "silverstream_s", "author_bot": false, "content": "提到奥尔拉就不得不讲她被改的特效，尤其是那华丽的大招，没了！\n\n首先讲技能。\n奥尔拉和别的唤醒体不一样的地方在于“打击”和“防御”比较特殊，与2个技能组成了一套情绪，分别对应喜怒哀惧。在迁跃时打出，生成的特效也随之改变。\n\n喜\njoyous\nadj.快乐的;高兴的;令人愉快的\n\n平等痛恨所有花体，看的时候第2个o特别像c，也特别像e，但是只有ous能组成喜悦的单词。", "timestamp": "2024-07-16T01:03:07.540000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1262575209660022794", "filename": "Image_1721091156967.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 705979, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1221527962495484015/1262575209660022794/Image_1721091156967.png?ex=69cc6ecb&is=69cb1d4b&hm=e998ca462ff9d626fdcb98e9ce1b56931dde48ed4147c246635dccbc3f6a4c54&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1221527962495484015", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "游戏美术资源上的文字", "forum_channel_id": "1181146739198140487"}
