{"id": "1262579540975292529", "channel_id": "1221527962495484015", "type": 0, "author_id": "1168864875943055370", "author_name": "silverstream_s", "author_bot": false, "content": "除了角色小人身上环绕的特效，部分技能释放时也有出现特效文字。\n\n喜（幻梦诗篇）/灵知觉醒（诗册序言）\nle jardin est um mythe \net les roses sont ses iéponses\n这两句法语连起来就是（机翻：\n花园是神话，玫瑰是它的果实", "timestamp": "2024-07-16T01:20:20.162000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-07-16T01:47:18.065000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1262579540954447934", "filename": "Image_1721092691576.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 301665, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1221527962495484015/1262579540954447934/Image_1721092691576.png?ex=69cc72d4&is=69cb2154&hm=7fcc5259e315d22bac353baed3f8499ece7b4df9f60847510aac42b81bf9cf58&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1221527962495484015", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "游戏美术资源上的文字", "forum_channel_id": "1181146739198140487"}
