{"id": "1262745855207669800", "channel_id": "1221527962495484015", "type": 0, "author_id": "1168864875943055370", "author_name": "silverstream_s", "author_bot": false, "content": "噢噢美术组发了奥尔拉小人的设定图。\n机器翻译了一下，和命轮上面的字一样：https://discord.com/channels/1131791637933199470/1221527962495484015/1221565577785638982\n\nil n'est\npas mort…\nAlors…alors…\nil va donc falloir\nque je me tue，moi ！…\n他不是\n没有死……\n所以……所以……\n因此，必须\n让我自杀吧！……", "timestamp": "2024-07-16T12:21:12.565000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-07-16T12:21:56.813000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1262745854138253345", "filename": "img-1721131659457f196a6b1e91c64c184de1b62b66b123bc9c315655ffdf5c7ef849252053f9b95.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 63678, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1221527962495484015/1262745854138253345/img-1721131659457f196a6b1e91c64c184de1b62b66b123bc9c315655ffdf5c7ef849252053f9b95.jpg?ex=69cc64f8&is=69cb1378&hm=39a61be9a18b3a9dfbee637129c42daccaa258cfdf8df48e0a9abc5ca74bed69&"}, {"id": "1262745854964662323", "filename": "Image_1721132262368.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 885892, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1221527962495484015/1262745854964662323/Image_1721132262368.png?ex=69cc64f8&is=69cb1378&hm=f7149b77d7e17b5c6ad3c16b54bc92aa1ff9dedf54b7e540c45858103fe593f9&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1221527962495484015", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "游戏美术资源上的文字", "forum_channel_id": "1181146739198140487"}
{"id": "1262746732308201562", "channel_id": "1221527962495484015", "type": 0, "author_id": "1168864875943055370", "author_name": "silverstream_s", "author_bot": false, "content": "正式版本都把老设定改掉了，但是小人和命轮都没改。而且这段话有些没头没尾的，而且原作也是一点不记得，对这边“他没有死，所以我必须自杀”理解不能。", "timestamp": "2024-07-16T12:24:41.682000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-07-16T12:31:36.579000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1221527962495484015", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "游戏美术资源上的文字", "forum_channel_id": "1181146739198140487"}
